== Purpose ==
Sometimes articles have both Commons articles and categories about them. This template can be used to generate an inline link to a [[commons:Commons:Galleries|Commons gallery]] and a [[commons:Commons:Categories|Commons category]]. It is intended for use in the "[[Wikipedia:External links|External links]]" section of an article.

== Usage ==
This template is for usage when both the Commons article page and category page are the same. There is also an optional parameter for {{para|extratext}}.

===Example===
*{{tlx|commons and category-inline|<var>Ursus maritimus</var>}}

yields: 

*{{commons and category-inline|Ursus maritimus}}

